{"tid":1646090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"為左你地既國家，五毛們請你地自首","createTime":"2019-10-11T07:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T13:48:31.000Z","uid":277644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c27868c7053fe865fb874e7b79078bcd380d9b07","tid":1646090,"uid":277644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T07:01:54.000Z","msg":"根據《中華人民共和國計算機信息網絡國際聯網管理暫行規定》（下稱《暫行規定》）第六條，「計算機信息網絡直接進行國際聯網，必須使用郵電部國家公用電信網提供的國際出入口信道。任何單位和個人不得自行建立或者使用其他信道進行國際聯網」。公安機關可對違反此規定的人給予警告，並處以最高15000元罰款。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-46823319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-46823319&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=27ddeda6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-46823319&h=728daba8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-46823319</a><br />\n<br />\n根據2019年8月既數據，內地失業率上升至5.3%較上一個月高0.7%，直接反映支那經濟下滑。國難當前，支那五毛責無旁貸。<br />\n保守估計內地至少有1千萬既活躍五毛，假如首次罰款係1000蚊，將可為國庫帶黎100億既收入，不過作為愛國五毛，我地義不容辭直接比15000（姐係1500億）（不過五毛好似降價降到一毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），相信定必可以為國家雪中送炭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n國家與金錢，相信五毛永遠會站起國家既一邊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我是五毛，你可以收我15000了。</span></span>"},{"pid":"dd9ac86f61326ed211814cf05f4f7fb133d7c398","tid":1646090,"uid":277644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T07:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d407aaa13e018b5f2f8bf12a7f0e952074ef63","tid":1646090,"uid":125958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T13:48:31.000Z","msg":"推"}]}